  {
    "type": "EXPOSITORY (ENGLISH BIBLE)",
    "name": "Jamieson-Fausset-Brown Bible Commentary",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "3-6. saw … evidently—\"distinctly.\"",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "the ninth hour of the day—three o'clock, the hour of the evening sacrifice. But he had been \"fasting until that hour\" (Ac 10:30), perhaps from the sixth hour (Ac 10:9).",
        "children": []
      }
    ]
