        "element": "span",
        "class": "ital",
        "text": "as it were about the ninth hour",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Circumstantiality of expression. See Bornemann ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
